title: Lyrical Genius vs Snapping ( Isaiah Rashad Interview)
itunes:title: Lyrical Genius vs Snapping ( Isaiah Rashad Interview)
description:
Today on the show we had one of TDE's very own Isaiah Rashad stop by where he breaks down themes In 'The House Is Burning', speaks on Lyrical Miracle Rappers and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a Florida woman who threw her ex’s cat into a river during a fight, and was arrested for animal cruelty, can you guess what race she is? Also, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
